Package: btcecho
Title: Analysis functions used by BTC-ECHO for research purposes. 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Philipp", "Giese", email = "philipp.giese@btc-echo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package features various routines to get, analyze and visualize cryptocurrency-related data. Routines to get info from several APIs such as coinmarketcrap, coingecko, cryptocompare, coincap etc are provided. One important part is, beside data cleaning,portfolio analytics and visualization. 
Depends: R (>= 3.4.4)
